name: Plated Cushion
description: Indulge your modern aesthetics with luxe texture and piped details with our silver grey velvet cushion cover. Team with our curated collection of black and white cushions for a look that’s refined and unmatched.

name: Silver Cushion
description: This grey faux fur cushion cover will bring some bling to your look or create a sense of opulence. Soft, fluffy and perfect for contemporary styles especially Scandi styling.

name: Deep Blue Cushion
description: Mid to dark shades of blue feel trendy, but sophisticated enough to lend a timeless feel. If you’re looking to show off vivid colours, this Albany royal blue cushion cover is the perfect piece for a bold focal point.

name: Pink Cushion
description: This lovely light pink fluffy cushion cover is perfect for lush styling of your home. A perfect pairing with chocolate and navy tones, the soft look and feel is a luxurious addition to any contemporary decor.

name: Black Cushion
description: Faux fur adds a cosy touch that’s perfect for the winter, but can lend a daring vibe suitable for the warmer season. In daring black, this fur cushion cover will add much needed elegance all-year round.

name: Green Cushion
description: Soft, natural colours that are easy to decorate with often lend a sense of calm to a space. In an ultimate destressing colour, this Albany sage green rectangular cushion is an ideal piece for a soothing and restful vibe.
